.TH WEBMAP_CREATE 3 "2026-07-15" "libwebmap" "Library Functions"
.SH NAME
webmap_create, webmap_create_with_config, webmap_destroy \- create a web map context
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #include <webmap.h>
.PP
.B webmap_ctx_t *webmap_create(void);
.B webmap_ctx_t *webmap_create_with_config(const webmap_config_t *cfg);
.B void webmap_destroy(webmap_ctx_t *ctx);
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Allocate a map context that holds basemap tiles and dynamic overlays for a
WebGPU-oriented status map. The library performs no I/O; the host feeds
.B .wmap
tiles and overlay updates.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR webmap_load_wmap_tile (3),
.BR webmap_upsert_overlay (3),
.BR webmap_next_event (3)
